<h2 id="authentication">Authentication</h2>

<p>You must pass a token to each API endpoint. Refer to the right to get an access token. The access
 token is expected as-is on the <code class="prettyprint">Authorization</code> header of each request.</p>

<blockquote>
<p>Log in to your CF api</p>
</blockquote>
<pre class="highlight shell"><code>cf api http://api.MY-INSTALLATION.com
</code></pre>

<blockquote>
<p>Get an access token</p>
</blockquote>
<pre class="highlight shell"><code>cf oauth-token
</code></pre>
